# API Automation Testing Standards

## API Discovery Rules

* Swagger/OpenAPI specification URL:

  * `https://fakerestapi.azurewebsites.net/swagger/v1/swagger.json`

* Always parse and validate the Swagger/OpenAPI specification before test generation.

* Automatically discover all Controllers, Endpoints, Methods, Parameters, Request Bodies, Response Schemas, Status Codes, and Security Requirements.

* Generate tests for every endpoint defined in the specification.

* Detect newly added endpoints and automatically include them in test coverage.

* Validate that Swagger definitions match actual API responses.

---

# Test Framework Rules

## Technology Stack

* Use Playwright Test Runner for API testing.
* Use Playwright APIRequestContext for all API calls.
* Use TypeScript.
* Use async/await throughout the framework.
* Follow Page Object Model principles adapted for API testing (API Client Layer).
* Enable strict TypeScript mode.
* Use ESLint and Prettier standards.
* Save Swagger URL and Auth tokens in separate config files

